story.text: Got sworn into the Montana Bar yesterday! Whoop! I am glad I was here this weekend to help out Kerr with her breakup with Eric. I think this has been a very rough time for her.
Today I am feeling sick again - this has been the cold from hell. I wonder if I have cancer or something crazy. Probably just need to lay off life for a min.
So smokey in Missoula. I hope climate change brings more moisture to the mountain west.
